set fire to the stars is a 2014 british semi-biographical drama film directed by andy goddard in his directorial debut . co-written by goddard and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; jones , the film stars elijah wood as poet john m. &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and jones as dylan thomas with supporting roles by kelly reilly , steven mackintosh , shirley henderson , and kevin eldon . the film was released in the united kingdom on 7 november 2014 .